title: NOTOX - Demolished
description:
From http://www.notoxpunk.com/ :
"NOTOX is a Boston-based DIY hardcore punk band featuring guitarist Will Sullivan and drummer Sam Jodrey of TOXIC NARCOTIC. Joining them on bass is Pat Faherty.

Creating troubled music for troubled times, NOTOX delivers an all new blast of chaotic anthems about the rise, decline, and demise of the human race.  

NOTOX is currently booking local and national shows to coincide with their debut record DEMOLISHED."

This is that record. (DEMOLISHED, if you weren't paying attention).
